{
  "stem": "9701.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, when I was on the train, my parents were on the platform, and the windows of the compartment were open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were still chit chatting, sort of small talk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, like, my parents were telling me to be sure to be polite when I get to England, to say please and thank you, which were some of the few English words that I knew.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were trying to be cheerful, trying to smile.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as the train began to move out of the station, and I joined the transport, by the way, in Frankfurt, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they ran to the end of the platform.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I could see the tears streaming down their face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew, in that instant, that they really loved me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That this was a great sacrifice that they made because they loved me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That, in a way, they really gave me-- this is not what I was thinking then, but this act on their part really gave me life a second time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As the train was pulling out of the station, and they were running to the end of the platform, I was looking out of the window, and they were getting smaller and smaller.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally, they were just two dots, and then, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What I did not know at that time is that this was the last time I saw my parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I understand that he was very uncomfortable talking to me about sex education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm pretty sure that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you know, what does immortality, what is having-- you know, I mean, and the way he questioned me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, why is it-- why are they immortal?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
